---
title: "Sequence Diagram: Autentificare Utilizator"
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Utilizator
    participant UI as Login Component
    participant AuthService as Auth Service
    participant HTTP as HTTP Client
    participant API as /api/auth/login.php
    participant Model as Teacher/Student Model
    participant DB as MySQL Database

    User->>UI: Introduce email & parolă
    User->>UI: Click "Login"

    UI->>UI: Validare formular<br/>(email valid, parolă min 6 chars)

    alt Validare failed
        UI-->>User: Afișare eroare validare
    else Validare success
        UI->>AuthService: login(credentials)

        AuthService->>HTTP: POST /api/auth/login.php<br/>{email, password}

        HTTP->>API: HTTP Request

        API->>API: Verifică dacă email<br/>conține '@'

        alt Email fără '@'
            API->>API: Adaugă @academic.tuiasi.ro<br/>sau @student.tuiasi.ro
        end

        API->>Model: getByEmail(email)

        Model->>DB: SELECT * FROM teachers<br/>WHERE email = ?

        alt User găsit în teachers
            DB-->>Model: Record găsit
            Model-->>API: User data (cu password hash)

            API->>API: password_verify(input, hash)

            alt Password invalid
                API-->>HTTP: {success: false, error: "Invalid"}
                HTTP-->>AuthService: Error response
                AuthService-->>UI: Login failed
                UI-->>User: Mesaj: "Date incorecte"
            else Password valid
                API->>API: Generare token<br/>(base64 JSON)
                API-->>HTTP: {success: true,<br/>user: {...}, token: "..."}
                HTTP-->>AuthService: Success response

                AuthService->>AuthService: Salvare token în<br/>sessionStorage
                AuthService->>AuthService: Salvare user în<br/>sessionStorage

                AuthService-->>UI: Login success

                alt User is Admin
                    UI->>UI: Redirect /admin/dashboard
                else User is Teacher
                    UI->>UI: Redirect /teacher/dashboard
                end

                UI-->>User: Dashboard afișat
            end

        else User nu există în teachers
            API->>Model: Caută în students
            Model->>DB: SELECT * FROM students<br/>WHERE email = ?

            alt User găsit în students
                DB-->>Model: Record găsit
                Model-->>API: User data

                API->>API: password_verify(input, hash)

                alt Password valid
                    API->>API: Generare token
                    API-->>HTTP: Success + token
                    HTTP-->>AuthService: Login success
                    AuthService->>AuthService: Save session
                    AuthService-->>UI: Success
                    UI->>UI: Redirect /student/dashboard
                    UI-->>User: Dashboard afișat
                else Password invalid
                    API-->>HTTP: Error
                    HTTP-->>AuthService: Failed
                    AuthService-->>UI: Error
                    UI-->>User: "Date incorecte"
                end

            else User nu există nicăieri
                API-->>HTTP: {success: false,<br/>error: "User not found"}
                HTTP-->>AuthService: Error
                AuthService-->>UI: Failed
                UI-->>User: "Utilizator inexistent"
            end
        end
    end

    Note over User,DB: Token-ul este trimis în header-ul<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}<br/>la toate request-urile ulterioare
